Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zombíci.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mŕtvi, oživení pomocou čiernej mágie alebo elixírov,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}túžiaci po mäse a krvi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Najdesivejšie príšery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}V tomto malom japonskom mestečku sa takíto zombíci...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}objavili!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Och, to si len ty, Babu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prekvapil si ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ja som tiež zombík.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Už viac nie som nažive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:08.92,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the story I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:12.09,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,on that sleepless night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:17.09,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,was just a fairy tale.
